From f3b6fe564df229f6b0e848092e1d60a36c8108e8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Takagi Tasuku <tasuren@outlook.jp>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 12:31:16 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 12/14] Replace named channel bootstrap with inherited endpoint

Switch the CBF IPC bootstrap from NamedMojoIpcServer (named Unix
domain socket) to a Mojo PlatformChannel with inherited endpoint:

- CbfService: drop NamedMojoIpcServer; add mojo::Receiver bound from
  PlatformChannel::RecoverPassedEndpointFromCommandLine.
- bridge: add cbf_bridge_prepare_channel, cbf_bridge_pass_child_pid,
  cbf_bridge_client_connect_inherited; remove cbf_bridge_client_connect.
- cbf_bridge_support: add PendingChannel with handle_info for
  platform-specific handle passing (Mach ports on macOS, fd on Linux).
- BUILD.gn: drop //components/named_mojo_ipc_server dependency.
